                        <li>Appropriate technical and organizational measures shall be employed to safeguard my personal information against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, misuse, or destruction.</li>
                        <li>My personal information shall not be shared with any unauthorized third party without my consent, except when required by law.</li>
                        <li>The data gathered may be used for academic research, statistical analysis, and system improvement purposes. Any reports, presentations, or publications resulting from this study shall present only aggregated or anonymized information to ensure that my identity remains protected.</li>
